# Currency Converter - Spring Boot Project

This is a simple Currency Converter web application built using **Spring Boot**, **JSP**, and **Maven**.

## 🚀 Features
- Convert currencies using real-time exchange rates
- User-friendly JSP interface
- MVC architecture with Spring Boot

---

## 📝 Prerequisites
Before running the project, ensure you have the following installed:

- **Java JDK 8+**
- **Maven**
- **Git**
- **IDE (VS Code, IntelliJ, Eclipse, etc.)**

---

## ⚙️ Setup Instructions

1️⃣ **Clone the Repository:**  
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Abhinandan1822/CodSoft.git
cd CodSoft/currencyconverter
```

2️⃣ **Build the Project with Maven:**  
```bash
mvn clean install
```

3️⃣ **Run the Application:**  
```bash
mvn spring-boot:run
```
Or, if using an IDE, run `CurrencyconverterApplication.java` directly.

4️⃣ **Access the Application:**  
Open your browser and go to:
```bash
http://localhost:8080/jsps/converter.jsp
```

---

## 📁 Project Structure
```
currencyconverter/
├── src/main/java/com/biit/currencyconverter/
│   ├── controller/          # Handles HTTP requests
│   ├── model/               # Data models
│   ├── service/             # Business logic
│   └── CurrencyconverterApplication.java
├── src/main/resources/      # Application properties
├── src/main/webapp/jsps/    # JSP files (UI)
├── pom.xml                  # Maven configuration
└── README.md                # Project documentation
```

